high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove.
Pick up the plate from the stove.
Move to the right and face the sink.
Put the plate on the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Put the knife on the plate.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife on a plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to stand in front of the white stove.
Pick the pan up from the bottom left of the stove.
Turn to the right and stand facing the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the pan down on the counter to the right of the white plate.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Put the knife in the pan on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove top.
Pick up the pan from the stove top.
Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the pan on top of the counter, just below the knife.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Place the knife in the pan with it sticking straight up.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife in a pan on the counter top.
